data.description:
Big House/Large RV covering. 
Lots of Lots of Room! 
Excellent 55+Cul-de sac property with plenty of space for vehicles and RV, 2 bed 1.75 bath, large living room and dining room. Sunroom and additional covered space. Complete workshop with sink and lighting. 
2023 BRAND NEW A/C Unit under warranty.
Upgrades. All engineering certs current and available.  Kitchen has breakfast bar. Home has copper plumbing. Mesa East is a safe neighborhood, has lots of activities and is located near shopping and medical. Hwy 60 and Loop 202 close by make it easy to get around the Valley quickly. CASH or  FINANCING ACCEPTED.
